        "timestamp": "2018-08-23 07:30:03.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDraft has been raised for clamp and log respective changes so that they can use the logstash from common charts\n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/62001/\n\nAlso, idea is to take the configmaps from respective charts ..\n\nResults when logstash is used from common chart is as below :\n\nonap9         dev9-clamp-6f6c7b4b87-rhbmh                    2/2       Running             0          1h\nonap9         dev9-clamp-dash-es-6dd99bf56c-7zh9k            1/1       Running             0          1h\nonap9         dev9-clamp-dash-kibana-c6596c578-k5f9v         1/1       Running             0          1h\nonap9         dev9-clamp-logstash-sq526                      1/1       Running             0          1h\nonap9         dev9-clampdb-7997fcbfd8-fw4bd                  1/1       Running             0          1h\nonap9         dev9-log-elasticsearch-5f9777459c-24xlb        1/1       Running             0          1h\nonap9         dev9-log-kibana-5645cfbc75-ztjkf               1/1       Running             0          1h\nonap9         dev9-log-logstash-chjml                        1/1       Running             0          1h\n\nRegards,\nPriyanka Jain.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
